      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and is truly showroom quality. It has been meticulously maintained with no mechanical issues, a flawless exterior paint job, and a pristine interior that still feels brand new. Every feature works perfectly, making this an exceptional find for a collector or a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives like it just left the factory.",
